{{/* Concept-doc REACH line — a single honest descriptive note, rendered under
     the surface-tile grid. This is NOT the concept-doc coverage chip (there is
     none — the surface-tile row stays the existing fill-the-bar surfaces); it
     is a map of how far the project's narrative docs reach into the contract.
     Counts ONLY: clear (docs single this element out), ambiguous (named but
     never disambiguated from same-spelled kin), and "the rest" (not discussed
     in prose — the expected default). Deliberately no percentage, no bar, no
     fill: dividing "discussed" by "total contract" would invent a grade out of
     a map. Gated on ConceptDocConfigured so a repo with no concept-doc source
     wired renders nothing rather than a misleading "0 of N". */}}
{{define "vchip"}}{{if .Show}}<button type="button" class="vchip{{if .Alert}} alert{{end}}" data-vd="{{.Verdict}}" data-vg="{{.Glyph}}" data-vc="{{.Class}}" data-vs="{{.Surface}}" data-vnum="{{.Number}}" data-vprov="{{.Provenance}}" data-viss="{{.Issues}}" data-vrem="{{.Remediation}}">{{.Glyph}} {{.Verdict}}</button>{{end}}{{end}}
{{define "conceptDocReach"}}{{if .ConceptDocConfigured}}<div class="cd-reach"><span class="cd-reach-dot"></span><span>Concept docs clearly reference {{if .ConceptDocsHref}}<a class="cd-reach-link" href="{{.ConceptDocsHref}}"><b>{{.ConceptDocClear}}</b> of <b>{{.Total}}</b> {{if eq .Total 1}}entity{{else}}entities{{end}}{{if .ConceptDocAmbiguous}}; <b>{{.ConceptDocAmbiguous}}</b> named ambiguously{{end}}</a>{{else}}<b>{{.ConceptDocClear}}</b> of <b>{{.Total}}</b> {{if eq .Total 1}}entity{{else}}entities{{end}}{{if .ConceptDocAmbiguous}}; <b>{{.ConceptDocAmbiguous}}</b> named ambiguously{{end}}{{end}}<span class="cd-reach-rest">; the rest aren&rsquo;t discussed in narrative docs (expected).</span></span></div>{{end}}{{end}}
